1
00:00:08,144 --> 00:00:10,177
[ GROWLING ]

2
00:00:15,144 --> 00:00:16,877
PAKU!

3
00:00:17,977 --> 00:00:21,810
PAKU, YOU'RE THE ONLY FRIEND
I EVER HAD.

4
00:00:22,744 --> 00:00:25,644
I'LL PROTECT YOU!
NO.

5
00:00:25,677 --> 00:00:28,944
IZUMO, YOU KNOW WHAT?

6
00:00:30,744 --> 00:00:33,110
THE TRUTH IS I DON'T LIKE YOU.

7
00:00:33,144 --> 00:00:35,110
[ GASPS ]

8
00:00:36,844 --> 00:00:39,344
YOU ARE NOT WORTHY
OF OUR HELP.

9
00:00:44,010 --> 00:00:45,277
[ GRUNTS ]

10
00:00:45,310 --> 00:00:47,244
[ GROWLING ]

11
00:00:47,277 --> 00:00:49,644
[ SCREAMS ]

12
00:00:49,677 --> 00:00:52,410
[ GASPS, PANTING ]

13
00:00:56,510 --> 00:00:58,310
A DREAM.

14
00:01:03,177 --> 00:01:05,344
HOW STUPID.

15
00:01:14,677 --> 00:01:17,944
♪ [ MAN SINGING
IN JAPANESE ]

16
00:02:42,003 --> 00:02:44,936
[ GRUMBLING ]

17
00:02:44,969 --> 00:02:46,736
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

18
00:02:47,836 --> 00:02:49,703
GOOD MORNING.

19
00:02:49,736 --> 00:02:52,003
HEY. GOOD MORNING.

20
00:02:54,303 --> 00:02:56,136
[ SPITS ]

21
00:02:56,169 --> 00:02:57,903
[ FAUCET SQUEAKS ]
[ WATER SPLASHING ]

22
00:02:57,936 --> 00:02:59,369
LISTEN.
HMM?

23
00:03:00,503 --> 00:03:03,136
DON'T YOU DARE TELL ANYONE
I WAS CRYING.

24
00:03:03,169 --> 00:03:04,936
NOT A SOUL.
UNDERSTAND?

25
00:03:04,969 --> 00:03:07,503
WHO, ME?
WHY WOULD I DO THAT?

26
00:03:07,536 --> 00:03:09,569
JUST PROMISE YOU'LL KEEP
YOUR MOUTH SHUT, OKAY?

27
00:03:09,603 --> 00:03:12,336
I'M NOT GONNA TELL ANYONE,
SO CHILL OUT.

28
00:03:13,903 --> 00:03:16,236
[ GARGLING ]
HERE.

29
00:03:16,269 --> 00:03:18,069
THANKS A LOT.

30
00:03:22,736 --> 00:03:26,669
IF YOU HADN'T SHOWN UP,
WHO KNOWS WHAT WOULD'VE
HAPPENED TO PAKU AND ME.

31
00:03:26,703 --> 00:03:29,436
SO, ANYWAY, THANKS A LOT
FOR DOING THAT.

32
00:03:29,469 --> 00:03:32,403
OH, SWEET!
YOU WASHED IT FOR ME.

33
00:03:32,436 --> 00:03:35,803
- HUH?
- OH, MAN, I WAS
SO WRONG ABOUT YOU.

34
00:03:35,836 --> 00:03:37,236
YOU ROCK, YOU KNOW THAT?

35
00:03:37,269 --> 00:03:41,069
WRONG! I ONLY WASHED IT
'CAUSE IT WAS STINKY.

36
00:03:41,103 --> 00:03:43,836
SERIOUSLY?
WAS IT REALLY STINKY?

37
00:03:43,869 --> 00:03:45,103
[ YUKIO ]
GOOD MORNING.

38
00:03:45,136 --> 00:03:47,836
MR. OKUMURA.

39
00:03:50,236 --> 00:03:53,503
THAT FEVER YOU'VE GOT
WILL BE GONE
IN ABOUT TWO OR THREE DAYS.

40
00:03:53,536 --> 00:03:55,703
YOU'LL BE UP AND ABOUT SOON.

41
00:03:55,736 --> 00:03:58,136
REST UP, OKAY?

42
00:03:58,169 --> 00:04:01,203
THANKS A LOT FOR EVERYTHING,
MR. OKUMURA.

43
00:04:01,236 --> 00:04:03,903
- TAKE IT EASY NOW.
- YEAH, I WILL.

44
00:04:03,936 --> 00:04:05,603
THANKS A LOT, RIN.

45
00:04:05,636 --> 00:04:08,269
YOU FIND ANYTHING OUT
ABOUT THAT THING
THAT ATTACKED US?

46
00:04:08,303 --> 00:04:12,369
I KNOW IT WAS A MID-LEVEL CLASS
OF NABERIUS DEMON.

47
00:04:12,403 --> 00:04:14,403
I'M STILL TRYING TO FIGURE OUT
HOW IT GOT IN THOUGH.

48
00:04:14,436 --> 00:04:18,603
WAIT, YOU SAID THE ACADEMY HAD
ALL THESE SPELLS AND CHARMS
THAT KEPT DEMONS OUT.

49
00:04:18,636 --> 00:04:21,303
WOW, YOU REMEMBERED.
THAT'S IMPRESSIVE.

50
00:04:21,336 --> 00:04:23,503
COME ON, STOP MESSING AROUND.

51
00:04:23,536 --> 00:04:25,703
YOU'RE RIGHT
ABOUT THE SPELLS.

52
00:04:25,736 --> 00:04:28,969
BUT SOMETIMES THAT KIND OF DEMON
SLIPS THROUGH.

53
00:04:29,003 --> 00:04:32,369
IT'S IMPORTANT WE KEEP
OUR GUARD UP FROM NOW ON.

54
00:04:33,503 --> 00:04:35,736
[ GIGGLES ]
ISN'T RIN THE BEST?

55
00:04:35,769 --> 00:04:38,169
HE SEEMS LIKE
HE'S PRETTY COOL.

56
00:04:38,203 --> 00:04:40,136
AND DON'T YOU THINK
HE'S CUTE?

57
00:04:40,169 --> 00:04:43,603
HUH? HE-HE'S WHAT?
ARE YOU CRAZY?

58
00:04:43,636 --> 00:04:46,703
I THINK MR. OKUMURA'S
PRETTY COOL TOO.

59
00:04:46,736 --> 00:04:49,869
THEY'RE SUPPOSED TO BE TWINS,
BUT THEY COULDN'T BE
ANY MORE DIFFERENT.

60
00:04:49,903 --> 00:04:51,869
[ GIGGLES ]

61
00:04:55,036 --> 00:04:57,769
PAKU--
IZUMO, I--

62
00:04:57,803 --> 00:05:00,236
I DECIDED I'M GOING TO QUIT
THE CRAM SCHOOL.

63
00:05:00,269 --> 00:05:01,703
[ GASPS ]

64
00:05:01,736 --> 00:05:03,036
[ SIGHS ]

65
00:05:04,369 --> 00:05:05,969
I-I'M SORRY.

66
00:05:06,003 --> 00:05:07,803
WHY?
WHAT FOR?

67
00:05:07,836 --> 00:05:11,669
I'M SORRY FOR NOT BEING
A NICER PERSON.

68
00:05:11,703 --> 00:05:15,136
HMM. OH, WHAT ARE
YOU TALKING ABOUT?

69
00:05:15,169 --> 00:05:19,703
I FIGURED OUT THAT GOING
TO THIS CRAM SCHOOL ISN'T RIGHT
FOR ME, THAT'S ALL.

70
00:05:19,736 --> 00:05:23,369
IT'S NOT GOING
TO CHANGE THE FACT
THAT YOU AND I ARE FRIENDS.

71
00:05:23,403 --> 00:05:26,636
COME ON NOW.
DON'T GIVE ME THAT MOPEY LOOK.

72
00:05:26,669 --> 00:05:30,103
THE TRUTH IS, I LIKE YOU
JUST THE WAY YOU ARE.

73
00:05:30,136 --> 00:05:31,903
I MEAN IT.

74
00:05:39,303 --> 00:05:41,469
I ONLY DO...

75
00:05:41,503 --> 00:05:45,269
AS MY MASTER
COMMANDS ME TO.

76
00:05:45,303 --> 00:05:47,436
HIS MASTER.

77
00:05:47,469 --> 00:05:49,336
WHO IS HE TALKING ABOUT?

78
00:05:49,369 --> 00:05:50,969
I THOUGHT HE MEANT SATAN,

79
00:05:51,003 --> 00:05:55,836
BUT I HAVE NO IDEA WHY SATAN
WOULD WANNA KILL ME NOW.

80
00:05:55,869 --> 00:06:00,269
DEMONS OF ALL SPECIES
WILL COME AFTER YOU
FOR EVERY KIND OF REASON.

81
00:06:00,303 --> 00:06:02,003
DAMN IT.

82
00:06:02,036 --> 00:06:06,436
IF THEY'RE AFTER ME,
WHY'D THEY ATTACK
MY CLASSMATES?

83
00:06:06,469 --> 00:06:07,836
- RIN?
- [ GROANS ]

84
00:06:07,869 --> 00:06:10,269
[ BOTH SHOUTING ]

85
00:06:10,303 --> 00:06:13,769
HEY, DON'T GET UP
IN MY FACE LIKE THAT.

86
00:06:13,803 --> 00:06:17,403
IF I DID,
WHY'D YOU SIT UP SO FAST?
DUMMY.

87
00:06:17,436 --> 00:06:20,369
OOH! STOP MOVING ALREADY.

88
00:06:20,403 --> 00:06:23,603
IT'S OKAY.
I CAN HANDLE IT MYSELF
FROM HERE.

89
00:06:23,636 --> 00:06:26,236
[ GROANING ]

90
00:06:26,269 --> 00:06:27,903
[ SIGHS ]

91
00:06:27,936 --> 00:06:31,103
LEVEL WITH ME.
WHAT'S UP WITH YOU WASHING
EVERYONE'S SHEETS?

92
00:06:31,136 --> 00:06:33,336
WELL, I WANTED
TO DO SOMETHING,

93
00:06:33,369 --> 00:06:34,969
AND SINCE I'M GOOD
AT DOING LAUNDRY,

94
00:06:35,003 --> 00:06:38,036
I SORT OF THOUGHT THIS IS
ONE WAY I CAN HELP OUT TOO.

95
00:06:38,069 --> 00:06:39,603
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, TOO?

96
00:06:39,636 --> 00:06:42,336
YOU KNOW HOW YOU'RE
ALL WORKING HARD
TO BECOME EXORCISTS?

97
00:06:42,369 --> 00:06:44,836
THAT'S DOING SOMETHING
TO HELP OTHERS, ISN'T IT?

98
00:06:44,869 --> 00:06:48,136
I GUESS.
DOES THAT MEAN
YOU CHANGED YOUR MIND AND STUFF?

99
00:06:48,169 --> 00:06:51,036
I MEAN, DO YOU WANNA BE
AN EXORCIST NOW?

100
00:06:51,069 --> 00:06:53,503
OH, I DON'T KNOW.
ALTHOUGH--

101
00:06:55,669 --> 00:06:58,836
RIGHT NOW I'M GOOD AT LAUNDRY,
SO I'LL START THERE.

102
00:07:01,629 --> 00:07:04,063
[ WOMAN ]
MOST DEMONS CAN BE DESTROYED...

103
00:07:04,096 --> 00:07:06,663
BY RECITING WHAT ARE KNOWN
AS FATAL VERSES.

104
00:07:06,696 --> 00:07:11,763
THESE PASSAGES CONTAIN
CERTAIN WORDS OR PHRASES
THAT WILL CAUSE THEIR DEATH.

105
00:07:11,796 --> 00:07:16,963
IN BATTLE, ARIAS CAN IDENTIFY
AND RECITE THE CORRECT
FATAL VERSES AGAINST DEMONS.

106
00:07:16,996 --> 00:07:23,363
AND NOW WHAT BRAVE SOUL MAY I
CALL ON TO RECITE THE PASSAGE
I ASSIGNED FOR HOMEWORK?

107
00:07:23,396 --> 00:07:25,329
MISS KAMIKI?

108
00:07:25,363 --> 00:07:27,796
[ SIGHS ]
MISS KAMIKI,

109
00:07:27,829 --> 00:07:29,929
IS SOMETHING THE MATTER?

110
00:07:29,963 --> 00:07:33,129
I'M SORRY.
U-UM--

111
00:07:33,163 --> 00:07:35,129
THE TE DEUM, DEAR.

112
00:07:35,163 --> 00:07:36,829
FROM WHERE WE LEFT OFF,
PLEASE.

113
00:07:36,863 --> 00:07:38,729
OH, RIGHT.

114
00:07:38,763 --> 00:07:43,596
"DAY BY DAY WE MAGNIFY THEE,
AND WE WORSHIP THY NAME--

115
00:07:43,629 --> 00:07:45,729
THY NAME AND EVER WORLD--

116
00:07:48,163 --> 00:07:50,763
EVER WORLD"--
WHAT'S WRONG, DEAR?

117
00:07:50,796 --> 00:07:53,396
HUH?
I DON'T REMEMBER.

118
00:07:54,596 --> 00:07:56,363
OH, MY!

119
00:07:56,396 --> 00:08:00,029
MISS KAMIKI,
THIS ISN'T LIKE YOU AT ALL.

120
00:08:00,063 --> 00:08:03,063
LET'S SEE,
HOW ABOUT YOU, MR. SUGURO?

121
00:08:03,096 --> 00:08:07,963
YES, MA'AM.
DAY BY DAY, WE MAGNIFY THEE.

122
00:08:07,996 --> 00:08:10,729
AND WE WORSHIP THY NAME,
EVER WORLD WITHOUT END.

123
00:08:10,763 --> 00:08:15,563
VOUCHSAFE, O LORD,
TO KEEP US THIS DAY WITHOUT SIN.

124
00:08:15,596 --> 00:08:19,296
O LORD, HAVE MERCY UPON US,
HAVE MERCY UPON US.

125
00:08:19,329 --> 00:08:24,096
O LORD, LET THY MERCY
LIGHTEN UPON US
AS OUR TRUST IS IN THEE.

126
00:08:24,129 --> 00:08:26,296
O LORD, IN THEE HAVE I TRUSTED.

127
00:08:26,329 --> 00:08:29,063
LET ME NEVER BE CONFOUNDED.

128
00:08:29,096 --> 00:08:31,463
THAT WAS ABSOLUTELY PERFECT!

129
00:08:31,496 --> 00:08:32,796
WHOA!

130
00:08:32,829 --> 00:08:34,696
[ BELLS CHIMING ]

131
00:08:34,729 --> 00:08:36,163
[ SHIEMI ]
AMAZING.

132
00:08:36,196 --> 00:08:37,963
THAT WAS INCREDIBLE.

133
00:08:37,996 --> 00:08:40,496
EASY NOW.
DON'T START FALLING FOR ME.

134
00:08:40,529 --> 00:08:43,829
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.
YOU REALLY ARE SMART, MAN.

135
00:08:43,863 --> 00:08:45,829
WHAT'S THAT SUPPOSED TO MEAN?

136
00:08:45,863 --> 00:08:48,729
WELL, THE TRUTH IS,
IT'S NOT THAT BON'S
REALLY SMART.

137
00:08:48,763 --> 00:08:50,296
HE'S JUST GOOD
AT MEMORIZING.

138
00:08:50,329 --> 00:08:52,863
SO IN OTHER WORDS,
I AM SMART.

139
00:08:52,896 --> 00:08:54,729
ISN'T THAT RIGHT,
KONEKOMARU?

140
00:08:54,763 --> 00:08:56,296
UH, YES.

141
00:08:56,329 --> 00:08:59,163
WHATEVER.
MEMORIZING IS SOMETHING
ANYONE CAN DO.

142
00:08:59,196 --> 00:09:01,529
HUH? YOU WANT TO REPEAT
WHAT YOU SAID?

143
00:09:01,563 --> 00:09:04,663
- BON!
- HMM, BIG TALK
COMING FROM SOMEONE...

144
00:09:04,696 --> 00:09:07,663
- WHO CAN'T MEMORIZE
FOUR SENTENCES.
- OH, YEAH?

145
00:09:07,696 --> 00:09:10,463
IT'S NOT THAT I COULDN'T
MEMORIZE THEM.
I CHOSE NOT TO.

146
00:09:10,496 --> 00:09:13,763
ARIAS ARE COMPLETELY
DEFENSELESS
WHEN THEY'RE RECITING.

147
00:09:13,796 --> 00:09:15,929
THEIR PARTY
HAS TO PROTECT THEM.

148
00:09:15,963 --> 00:09:17,796
THEY'RE NOTHING BUT A BURDEN.

149
00:09:17,829 --> 00:09:19,429
WHAT THE HELL?

150
00:09:19,463 --> 00:09:22,329
YOU KNOW I WANNA BE ONE, AND
YOU DIS ME LIKE THAT, HUH?
BON!

151
00:09:22,363 --> 00:09:26,063
I'M SO SCARED.
WHAT, ARE YOU GONNA
BEAT ME UP NOW?

152
00:09:26,096 --> 00:09:28,529
YOU GOT NERVE MAKING FUN
OF PEOPLE'S DREAMS.

153
00:09:28,563 --> 00:09:31,729
HELL, THE FIRST DAY OF CLASS,
I KNEW YOU SUCKED.

154
00:09:31,763 --> 00:09:35,129
DREAMS?
OH, YOU MEAN THAT THING
ABOUT DEFEATING SATAN?

155
00:09:35,163 --> 00:09:39,329
HA! I DON'T KNOW ABOUT YOU,
BUT WHEN I HEAR
A JOKE LIKE THAT, I LAUGH.

156
00:09:39,363 --> 00:09:41,229
YEAH? THEN HOW ABOUT YOU?

157
00:09:41,263 --> 00:09:45,029
LET'S HAVE IT.
WHY DO YOU WANNA BE
AN EXORCIST? WELL?

158
00:09:45,063 --> 00:09:47,463
WHY DO I--

159
00:09:53,263 --> 00:09:56,563
I DON'T GO AROUND
TELLING EVERYONE
WHY I DO WHAT I DO...

160
00:09:56,596 --> 00:10:00,696
BECAUSE I'M NOT OUT TO GET
EVERYONE'S ATTENTION LIKE YOU.

161
00:10:00,729 --> 00:10:02,363
[ GROWLS ]
WHY YOU--

162
00:10:04,796 --> 00:10:06,029
OW.

163
00:10:06,063 --> 00:10:07,963
IF YOU'RE GONNA FIGHT,
GO OUTSIDE.

164
00:10:07,996 --> 00:10:10,096
[ YUKIO ]
SETTLE DOWN.

165
00:10:11,129 --> 00:10:13,663
ENOUGH WITH THE FIGHTING
ALREADY.

166
00:10:13,696 --> 00:10:15,196
[ DOG BARKING ]

167
00:10:15,229 --> 00:10:18,463
[ RIN ]
WHAT THE HELL'S UP
WITH THIS DAMN PICKLING ROCK?

168
00:10:18,496 --> 00:10:20,896
IT'S GETTING HEAVIER
BY THE SECOND.

169
00:10:20,929 --> 00:10:23,496
IT'S A DEMON,
ONE OF THE LOWER-LEVEL ONES.

170
00:10:23,529 --> 00:10:27,063
THE LONGER IT SITS ON YOU--
[ GRUNTS ]
THE HEAVIER IT GETS.

171
00:10:27,096 --> 00:10:29,163
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT A BARIYON IS?

172
00:10:29,196 --> 00:10:30,796
YOU REALLY ARE PATHETIC.

173
00:10:30,829 --> 00:10:33,629
OH, YEAH? WELL, IT'S YOUR FAULT
WE'RE HERE,
SO WHY DON'T YOU--

174
00:10:33,663 --> 00:10:35,929
IT'S EVERYONE'S FAULT.

175
00:10:35,963 --> 00:10:37,929
ONE OF THE OBJECTIVES
OF THIS BOOT CAMP...

176
00:10:37,963 --> 00:10:40,196
IS TO STRENGTHEN
YOUR ACADEMIC SKILLS.

177
00:10:40,229 --> 00:10:43,263
THE OTHER IS TO GET YOU
TO START BECOMING CLOSER
AS A TEAM.

178
00:10:43,296 --> 00:10:46,363
I'D RATHER DIE THAN BE FRIENDS
WITH THESE LOSERS.

179
00:10:46,396 --> 00:10:49,096
YOU NEED TO LEARN
TO GET ALONG.

180
00:10:49,129 --> 00:10:51,796
EXORCISTS DO NOT GO
INTO BATTLE ALONE.

181
00:10:54,863 --> 00:10:56,629
WE FIGHT IN GROUPS
OF TWO OR MORE.

182
00:10:56,663 --> 00:10:58,329
THAT'S BASIC PROCEDURE.

183
00:10:58,363 --> 00:11:00,763
IT COVERS YOUR WEAK SPOTS
AND ENHANCES YOUR STRENGTHS.

184
00:11:00,796 --> 00:11:04,163
IN A REAL COMBAT SITUATION,
THIS RIDICULOUS IN-FIGHTING...

185
00:11:04,196 --> 00:11:06,529
COULD GET YOU
OR SOMEONE ELSE KILLED.

186
00:11:06,563 --> 00:11:08,496
YOU KEEP THAT IN MIND.

187
00:11:08,529 --> 00:11:11,229
OKAY. I HAVE TO LEAVE
ON A MISSION,

188
00:11:11,263 --> 00:11:13,329
AND I WON'T BE BACK
FOR ABOUT THREE HOURS.

189
00:11:13,363 --> 00:11:17,129
NOW THEN, BECAUSE OF
THAT ATTACK YESTERDAY,

190
00:11:17,163 --> 00:11:18,896
I HAVE TO TAKE EXTRA MEASURES.

191
00:11:18,929 --> 00:11:20,563
I'LL BE LOCKING
ALL THE ENTRANCES...

192
00:11:20,596 --> 00:11:23,063
AND PLACING A POWERFUL
DEMON-WARDING CHARM
ON THE BUILDING.

193
00:11:23,096 --> 00:11:27,096
LOCKING US IN?
THEN HOW ARE WE SUPPOSED TO GET
OUT OF HERE IF WE NEED TO?

194
00:11:27,129 --> 00:11:29,063
YOU'RE NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

195
00:11:29,096 --> 00:11:31,963
I'LL ONLY BE GONE THREE HOURS.

196
00:11:31,996 --> 00:11:34,663
SO COOL OFF AND GET ALONG
UNTIL I GET BACK.

197
00:11:37,096 --> 00:11:39,929
THREE HOURS?
HE'S EVIL.

198
00:11:39,963 --> 00:11:41,663
SOMEONE KILL ME.

199
00:11:41,696 --> 00:11:45,463
YOU KNOW, I FIND IT HARD
TO BELIEVE YOU AND THAT
TEACHER ARE RELATED.

200
00:11:45,496 --> 00:11:48,496
[ STRAINING ]
BUT HE'S A GOOD GUY.
I KNOW HE IS.

201
00:11:48,529 --> 00:11:49,696
REALLY.

202
00:11:51,263 --> 00:11:54,329
ANYWAY, WE'RE STUCK HERE
THANKS TO A CERTAIN SOMEONE.

203
00:11:54,363 --> 00:11:57,663
HUH? I DIDN'T GO UP
AND GRAB YOU BY THE COLLAR,
DID I?

204
00:11:57,696 --> 00:12:00,396
YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO PICKED A FIGHT WITH ME
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

205
00:12:00,429 --> 00:12:02,996
WOULD YOU GUYS QUIT FIGHTING
WITH ME IN THE MIDDLE AGAIN?

206
00:12:03,029 --> 00:12:05,529
YOU'RE REALLY ONE TWISTED WITCH,
YOU KNOW THAT?

207
00:12:05,563 --> 00:12:09,196
THANKS FOR STATING THE OBVIOUS.
ANYTHING ELSE?

208
00:12:09,229 --> 00:12:11,729
WITH A PERSONALITY LIKE THAT,
NO WONDER YOU'RE ALL ALONE.

209
00:12:14,929 --> 00:12:16,363
[ SHIMA ]
WHAT THE--
[ SHIEMI SQUEALS ]

210
00:12:16,396 --> 00:12:18,729
[ RIN ]
OW! I DROPPED THE BARIYON
ON MY FOOT.

211
00:12:18,763 --> 00:12:21,963
YOU GOTTA BE KIDDING.
DID HE TURN THE LIGHTS OFF
ON THE WAY OUT?

212
00:12:21,996 --> 00:12:24,429
NO WAY!
IS IT A BLACKOUT?

213
00:12:24,463 --> 00:12:27,429
[ SHIMA ]
HUH-UH.
I CAN SEE LIGHTS ON OUTSIDE.

214
00:12:27,463 --> 00:12:30,663
[ RIN ]
YOU MEAN OUR BUILDING'S
THE ONLY ONE WITHOUT POWER?

215
00:12:30,696 --> 00:12:32,663
I'M GOING OUTSIDE.

216
00:12:32,696 --> 00:12:34,363
SHIMA, BE CAREFUL.

217
00:12:34,396 --> 00:12:37,063
[ CHUCKLES ]
I LOVE STUFF LIKE THIS.

218
00:12:37,096 --> 00:12:39,196
IT'S LIKE A REAL-LIFE TEST
OF COURAGE.

219
00:12:39,229 --> 00:12:42,063
[ CHUCKLES ]
THERE'S NOTHING HERE. SEE?

220
00:12:45,396 --> 00:12:47,696
MY EYES MUST BE
PLAYING TRICKS ON ME.

221
00:12:47,729 --> 00:12:50,729
EITHER THAT OR WE GOT A DE--
[ SCREAMING ]

222
00:12:52,796 --> 00:12:54,629
[ GROWLING ]

223
00:12:56,629 --> 00:12:58,096
NOT AGAIN.

224
00:13:09,051 --> 00:13:10,817
[ GROWLING ]

225
00:13:15,651 --> 00:13:17,084
THE GHOUL CAME BACK.

226
00:13:17,117 --> 00:13:19,051
WHAT ABOUT
THE DEMON-WARDING CHARM?

227
00:13:19,084 --> 00:13:21,617
[ SNARLS ]

228
00:13:21,651 --> 00:13:22,617
[ GASPS ]

229
00:13:26,451 --> 00:13:28,784
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?
EW, IT'S ITS FLUID.

230
00:13:33,251 --> 00:13:37,017
I'VE GOT TO DO SOMETHING.
I'VE GOT TO PROTECT EVERYONE.

231
00:13:37,051 --> 00:13:39,151
HEY, NEE?
NEE.

232
00:13:39,184 --> 00:13:40,784
I NEED MR. UNA-UNA.

233
00:13:40,817 --> 00:13:42,517
[ SQUEAKS ]

234
00:13:44,484 --> 00:13:46,217
[ ROARS ]

235
00:13:49,151 --> 00:13:52,217
[ SHIMA ]
OH, MY GOD.
[ RIN ] HOLY COW.

236
00:13:53,284 --> 00:13:56,251
THANK YOU, NEE.
YOU'RE THE BEST.
NEE!

237
00:13:56,284 --> 00:13:59,884
YOU SAVED US, SHIEMI.
THAT WAS QUICK THINKING.

238
00:13:59,917 --> 00:14:01,184
[ RUSTLING ]
HUH?

239
00:14:02,051 --> 00:14:03,717
[ CREAKING ]

240
00:14:10,517 --> 00:14:12,317
[ GROWLING ]

241
00:14:12,351 --> 00:14:14,684
IT'S TRYING
TO BREAK OUT OF THERE.

242
00:14:14,717 --> 00:14:17,751
DAMN IT. FOR A DEAD THING,
IT'S PRETTY LIVELY, ISN'T IT?

243
00:14:17,784 --> 00:14:20,917
THAT'S BECAUSE GHOULS
ARE MORE POWERFUL
IN THE DARKNESS.

244
00:14:20,951 --> 00:14:23,351
[ COUGHING ]

245
00:14:23,384 --> 00:14:25,951
WHAT'S THE MATTER,
SHIEMI?

246
00:14:25,984 --> 00:14:28,384
I'M FEELING DIZZY.

247
00:14:29,484 --> 00:14:30,951
[ COUGHING ]

248
00:14:30,984 --> 00:14:33,617
WHAT'S GOING ON?
I FEEL LIKE
I'M BURNING UP.

249
00:14:33,651 --> 00:14:37,284
- WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU GUYS?
- THAT GHOUL SPRAYED
ITS FLUID ALL OVER US.

250
00:14:37,317 --> 00:14:38,817
HOW COME YOU'RE NOT AFFECTED?

251
00:14:38,851 --> 00:14:42,784
I, UH--
COME ON, YUKIO.
WE NEED YOU HERE, DAMN IT.

252
00:14:42,817 --> 00:14:44,617
ONCE MORIYAMA
LOSES HER STRENGTH,

253
00:14:44,651 --> 00:14:46,484
THE BARRICADE SHE PUT UP
IS GONNA DISAPPEAR.

254
00:14:46,517 --> 00:14:48,784
THEN IT'S OVER FOR US.
[ BEEPING ]

255
00:14:48,817 --> 00:14:51,717
HELL OF A GOOD TIME
TO NOT BE PICKING UP, YUKIO.

256
00:14:51,751 --> 00:14:53,484
IT'S UP TO ME NOW.

257
00:14:53,517 --> 00:14:55,484
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

258
00:14:55,517 --> 00:14:57,884
I'M GONNA GO OUTSIDE
AND TRY TO DRAW IT AWAY.

259
00:14:57,917 --> 00:15:01,217
IF I CAN GET IT TO FOLLOW ME,
IT'LL GIVE YOU GUYS A CHANCE
TO GET OUT OF HERE.

260
00:15:01,251 --> 00:15:03,351
HUH?
HAVE YOU LOST YOUR MIND?

261
00:15:03,384 --> 00:15:05,284
HEY, YOU DON'T HAVE
TO WORRY ABOUT ME.

262
00:15:05,317 --> 00:15:06,917
I'M PRETTY STRONG, YOU KNOW.

263
00:15:06,951 --> 00:15:08,184
IDIOT.
HEY!

264
00:15:08,217 --> 00:15:10,584
OKUMURA!
COME BACK!

265
00:15:10,617 --> 00:15:12,484
[ MIWA ] OKUMURA!
[ SHIMA ]
DON'T DO IT.

266
00:15:14,917 --> 00:15:17,884
[ GROWLING ]

267
00:15:17,917 --> 00:15:21,351
I'M THE ONE YOU BASTARDS
ARE TRYING TO GET, RIGHT?
COME ON.

268
00:15:25,817 --> 00:15:27,951
THAT'S IT.
COME ON, BUDDY.

269
00:15:27,984 --> 00:15:30,351
MAN, THAT GUY'S CRAZY.

270
00:15:30,384 --> 00:15:32,651
WHA--
WE SHOULD GET OUT OF HERE
WHILE WE CAN.

271
00:15:32,684 --> 00:15:35,017
MISS MORIYAMA,
YOU CAN DROP THE BARRICADE NOW.

272
00:15:35,051 --> 00:15:37,184
HOLD ON.
LISTEN.

273
00:15:37,217 --> 00:15:38,584
DO YOU GUYS HEAR
ANYTHING?

274
00:15:38,617 --> 00:15:41,984
- HUH?
- [ RUSTLING ]

275
00:15:42,017 --> 00:15:43,717
[ GROWLING ]

276
00:15:43,751 --> 00:15:46,184
[ GASPS ]
NO WAY.
HUH-UH.

277
00:15:50,584 --> 00:15:54,351
THE LIGHTS. IF I CAN
TURN 'EM ON, THE GHOUL'S
GONNA LOSE ITS POWER.

278
00:15:57,384 --> 00:16:00,351
CAN'T JUST STAND AROUND
AND DO NOTHING.

279
00:16:00,384 --> 00:16:02,717
I'M GONNA RECITE A PASSAGE.

280
00:16:02,751 --> 00:16:05,951
BUT, BON, YOU DON'T EVEN
KNOW WHAT THAT THING'S
FATAL VERSE IS.

281
00:16:05,984 --> 00:16:08,817
YEAH, I KNOW THAT,
BUT FOR GHOUL-TYPE DEMONS
LIKE THIS ONE,

282
00:16:08,851 --> 00:16:12,117
ITS FATAL VERSE IS GONNA BE
SOMEWHERE IN THE GOSPEL OF JOHN.

283
00:16:12,151 --> 00:16:13,851
I'VE GOT THE WHOLE THING
MEMORIZED.

284
00:16:13,884 --> 00:16:16,984
IF I START RECITING IT,
I SHOULD COME ACROSS
THE RIGHT ONE AT SOME POINT.

285
00:16:17,017 --> 00:16:19,551
SERIOUSLY? BUT THERE'S LIKE
20 CHAPTERS IN IT.

286
00:16:19,584 --> 00:16:23,084
ACTUALLY, THERE'S 21.
IT'S NOT MUCH,

287
00:16:23,117 --> 00:16:27,217
BUT I'VE GOT CHAPTERS
ONE THROUGH 10 MEMORIZED.
SO IF YOU WANT, I CAN HELP.

288
00:16:27,251 --> 00:16:30,217
THANKS, KONEKOMARU.
LET'S DO THIS.

289
00:16:30,251 --> 00:16:32,717
HOLD ON A SECOND.
ONCE YOU START RECITING,

290
00:16:32,751 --> 00:16:34,884
THAT THING'S GOING TO FOCUS
ITS ATTACK ON YOU.

291
00:16:34,917 --> 00:16:38,551
WE DON'T HAVE TIME FOR THIS.
THAT GIRL'S BUSTING HER ASS
ALL BY HERSELF.

292
00:16:38,584 --> 00:16:40,917
A GUY CAN'T STAND HERE
AND DO NOTHING.

293
00:16:40,951 --> 00:16:43,651
THAT'S OUR BON.
WHAT A MAN.

294
00:16:46,451 --> 00:16:49,051
I DIDN'T MEMORIZE ANYTHING,
BUT I GOT THIS.

295
00:16:49,084 --> 00:16:51,284
ALL RIGHT.
THAT'S WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT.

296
00:16:51,317 --> 00:16:53,151
IF PUSH COMES TO SHOVE,
I'LL BACK YOU UP.

297
00:16:53,184 --> 00:16:54,951
Y-YOU GUYS ARE CRAZY.

298
00:16:54,984 --> 00:16:58,651
OH, YEAH? HEY, WEREN'T YOU
THE ONE ACTING ALL TOUGH
A LITTLE WHILE AGO?

299
00:16:58,684 --> 00:17:00,551
WHAT, CHICKENING
OUT NOW?

300
00:17:00,584 --> 00:17:03,351
[ GASPS ]
IF YOU WON'T FIGHT,
GET BACK.

301
00:17:04,551 --> 00:17:07,417
YOU START WITH CHAPTER ONE,
AND I'LL DO CHAPTER 11.

302
00:17:07,451 --> 00:17:09,651
BE CAREFUL YOU DON'T
GET THROWN OFF BY ME, OKAY?

303
00:17:09,684 --> 00:17:10,617
MM-HMM.

304
00:17:12,551 --> 00:17:14,517
HERE WE GO.
RIGHT.

305
00:17:14,551 --> 00:17:17,084
NOW A CERTAIN MAN WAS SICK.
LAZARUS--

306
00:17:19,351 --> 00:17:22,217
OKAY. IS THE POWER GRID IN HERE?

307
00:17:23,417 --> 00:17:24,617
THERE IT IS.

308
00:17:24,651 --> 00:17:27,984
ALL THE SWITCHES ARE OFF,
SO I'LL JUST FLIP 'EM BACK ON.

309
00:17:28,017 --> 00:17:29,317
[ RUSTLING ]

310
00:17:29,351 --> 00:17:31,651
- [ SHOUTS ]
- [ ROARING ]

311
00:17:46,084 --> 00:17:48,117
[ GASPING ]

312
00:17:51,051 --> 00:17:52,484
[ ROARING ]

313
00:17:52,517 --> 00:17:54,751
DON'T MESS WITH ME!

314
00:17:58,517 --> 00:18:02,317
[ INSTRUCTOR ]
EXCELLENT! THAT'S WHAT
I'VE BEEN WANTING TO SEE.

315
00:18:04,117 --> 00:18:07,051
THOSE BRILLIANT BLUE FLAMES
YOU KEEP HIDDEN.

316
00:18:07,084 --> 00:18:11,384
ARE YOU THE ONE WHO--
SINCE YOU WON'T USE YOUR POWERS
IN FRONT OF THE OTHERS,

317
00:18:11,417 --> 00:18:15,884
I DECIDED TO LURE YOU AWAY,
RIN OKUMURA--

318
00:18:15,917 --> 00:18:18,984
SON OF SATAN.

319
00:18:19,017 --> 00:18:21,351
[ SUGURO ]
LET NOT YOUR HEARTS
BE TROUBLED.

320
00:18:21,384 --> 00:18:23,751
BELIEVE IN GOD.
BELIEVE ALSO IN ME.

321
00:18:23,784 --> 00:18:26,284
[ GROWLING, POUNDING ]
WHEN THE SPIRIT
OF TRUTH COMES,

322
00:18:26,317 --> 00:18:28,284
HE SHALL GUIDE YOU
INTO ALL TRUTH.

323
00:18:28,317 --> 00:18:30,984
THIS BARRICADE WON'T HOLD
THAT MUCH LONGER.

324
00:18:31,017 --> 00:18:33,617
BON'S RECITING
THE LAST CHAPTER NOW.

325
00:18:35,417 --> 00:18:36,484
MORIYAMA!

326
00:18:36,517 --> 00:18:37,751
[ HISSING ]

327
00:18:37,784 --> 00:18:40,584
[ GROWLING ]

328
00:18:43,484 --> 00:18:45,984
DAMN YOU.

329
00:18:46,017 --> 00:18:50,584
AND WHEN HE HAD SPOKEN
THESE WORDS, HE SAID UNTO HIM,
"JUST KEEP FOLLOWING ME."

330
00:18:52,384 --> 00:18:56,317
HOW'D YOU FIND OUT?
WHO TOLD YOU ABOUT ME?

331
00:18:56,351 --> 00:18:57,784
[ CHUCKLES ]

332
00:18:57,817 --> 00:19:02,017
[ GASPS ]
ARE YOU THE SCUMBAG RESPONSIBLE
FOR THESE ATTACKS ON US?

333
00:19:02,051 --> 00:19:04,751
ACTUALLY, I AM.

334
00:19:04,784 --> 00:19:06,184
BUT ENOUGH ABOUT ME.

335
00:19:06,217 --> 00:19:08,784
I WANT TO SEE MORE
OF THAT POWER OF YOURS.

336
00:19:08,817 --> 00:19:10,784
- [ ROARS ]
- [ GROWLS ]

337
00:19:14,717 --> 00:19:16,684
I'M GONNA MAKE YOU PAY FOR THIS!

338
00:19:19,784 --> 00:19:22,151
[ GRUNTING ]

339
00:19:22,184 --> 00:19:24,784
JUST AS I THOUGHT.

340
00:19:30,351 --> 00:19:33,317
DAMN IT.
WHERE THE HELL DID HE GO?

341
00:19:34,284 --> 00:19:36,317
HEY, COME ON.
GET UP.

342
00:19:36,351 --> 00:19:39,351
MISS KAMIKI.
STAY WITH ME, OKAY?

343
00:19:39,384 --> 00:19:44,151
WHAT'S WRONG?
YOU'RE NOT LIKE
YOUR USUAL SELF... TODAY.

344
00:19:44,184 --> 00:19:46,917
- [ GASPS ]
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

345
00:19:46,951 --> 00:19:49,884
AM I ALL RIGHT?
SERIOUSLY?

346
00:19:49,917 --> 00:19:54,884
WHAT IS SHE SAYING?
WHY WOULD A KLUTZ LIKE HER
WORRY ABOUT ME?

347
00:19:54,917 --> 00:19:57,751
DAMN IT, BON.
HAVEN'T YOU FOUND IT YET?

348
00:19:57,784 --> 00:20:01,684
SHE'S RIGHT.
THERE IS SOMETHING WRONG
WITH ME.

349
00:20:01,717 --> 00:20:03,851
THIS ISN'T LIKE ME.

350
00:20:03,884 --> 00:20:07,284
I HUMBLY APPEAL TO THEE,
OH, GODDESS INARI.

351
00:20:07,317 --> 00:20:11,217
GRANT MY REQUEST.
LEAVE NOT MY PRAYERS
TO BE UNFULFILLED.

352
00:20:13,684 --> 00:20:15,917
HOW DARE YOU
SUMMON US AGAIN!

353
00:20:15,951 --> 00:20:17,584
HAVE YOU LEARNED
NOTHING?

354
00:20:17,617 --> 00:20:20,017
- YOU ARE NOT WORTHY--
- YOU WILL OBEY ME.

355
00:20:20,051 --> 00:20:22,917
[ GASPS ]
CURSES, SHE SNAPPED OUT OF IT.

356
00:20:22,951 --> 00:20:25,851
[ GRUNTS ]

357
00:20:25,884 --> 00:20:28,817
SO THE SAYING SPREAD ABROAD
AMONG THE BRETHREN.
BON!

358
00:20:28,851 --> 00:20:31,051
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE--

359
00:20:31,084 --> 00:20:33,951
I'VE GOT A BAD ATTITUDE,
AND I HATE LOSING.

360
00:20:33,984 --> 00:20:36,384
BUT THAT'S WHO I AM!

361
00:20:36,417 --> 00:20:38,651
...QUIVER AND NEVER LIVE AGAIN!
BEGONE, DEMON!

362
00:20:40,151 --> 00:20:43,784
- IT'S WORKING!
- [ GROWLING ]

363
00:20:43,817 --> 00:20:45,584
NO WAY.

364
00:20:45,617 --> 00:20:48,551
THIS IS THE DISCIPLE
WHO IS BEARING WITNESS
ABOUT THESE THINGS...

365
00:20:48,584 --> 00:20:50,484
AND WHO HAS WRITTEN
THESE THINGS.

366
00:20:50,517 --> 00:20:53,151
BON!
AND WE KNOW
THAT HIS TESTIMONY IS TRUE.

367
00:20:53,184 --> 00:20:54,917
- [ ROARS ]
- [ MIWA ]
THE LIGHTS.

368
00:20:54,951 --> 00:20:58,951
OF THE MANY THINGS JESUS DID,
WERE EVERY ONE OF THEM
TO BE WRITTEN,

369
00:20:58,984 --> 00:21:04,484
I SUPPOSE THAT THE WORLD ITSELF
COULD NOT CONTAIN THE BOOKS
THAT WOULD BE WRITTEN.

370
00:21:04,517 --> 00:21:06,517
[ ROARING ]

371
00:21:11,984 --> 00:21:13,817
BON!

372
00:21:13,851 --> 00:21:15,784
AM I DEAD? AM I?

373
00:21:15,817 --> 00:21:17,751
TELL ME.
BON.

374
00:21:17,784 --> 00:21:19,251
THANK GOD IT'S OVER.

375
00:21:19,284 --> 00:21:20,684
[ GRUNTING ]
HUH?

376
00:21:20,717 --> 00:21:25,051
HEY, WHAT HAPPENED
TO THE OTHER HALF
OF THE GHOUL THAT--

377
00:21:25,084 --> 00:21:28,551
BUT YOUR GHOUL-- WHAT HAPPENED?

378
00:21:28,584 --> 00:21:30,917
HUH?
OH, I KILLED IT.

379
00:21:30,951 --> 00:21:32,917
I GUESS YOU KILLED
YOURS TOO, HUH?

380
00:21:32,951 --> 00:21:34,784
AWESOME. HUH?
[ RUMBLING ]

381
00:21:36,651 --> 00:21:39,017
WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?
YOU WANNA GET KILLED?

382
00:21:39,051 --> 00:21:42,351
HEY, WAIT. STOP!
WHY DO YOU WANT TO KILL ME?

383
00:21:42,384 --> 00:21:43,984
YOU OKAY?

384
00:21:44,017 --> 00:21:46,417
YES. THANK YOU.

385
00:21:46,451 --> 00:21:49,751
LISTEN, I REALLY
DON'T LIKE YOU.

386
00:21:49,784 --> 00:21:51,551
[ GASPS ]
HUH?

387
00:21:51,584 --> 00:21:55,451
BUT YOU DID SAVE US TODAY,
SO-- SO THERE.

388
00:21:55,484 --> 00:21:56,784
UH-HUH.

389
00:22:01,284 --> 00:22:04,584
[ KAMIKI ]
PAKU, YOU KNOW WHAT?

390
00:22:04,617 --> 00:22:10,084
[ PAKU ]
IZUMO, THE TRUTH IS I LIKE YOU
JUST THE WAY YOU ARE.

391
00:22:10,117 --> 00:22:12,817
I MEAN IT.

392
00:22:12,851 --> 00:22:15,317
[ KAMIKI ]
I'LL DO MY BEST.
PROMISE.

393
00:22:19,517 --> 00:22:22,484
♪ [ MAN SINGING
IN JAPANESE ]

394
00:23:46,384 --> 00:23:48,751
[ SHOUTING ]
WHAT HAPPENED?

395
00:23:48,784 --> 00:23:51,751
HEY, YUKIO,
WHERE THE HELL
HAVE YOU BEEN? WE'VE--

396
00:23:51,784 --> 00:23:53,284
[ GASPS ]

397
00:23:53,317 --> 00:23:55,517
YOU.

398
00:24:03,184 --> 00:24:04,951
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

399
00:24:04,984 --> 00:24:06,484
[ INSTRUCTOR ]
AND THE PURPOSE OF IT ALL...

400
00:24:06,517 --> 00:24:09,984
IS TO GAIN AN ACCURATE READING
OF RIN OKUMURA'S CAPABILITIES.

401
00:24:10,017 --> 00:24:11,551
[ YUKIO ]
I'VE GOT A BAD FEELING
ABOUT THIS.

402
00:24:11,584 --> 00:24:13,517
[ SHIEMI ]
YUKI! RIN!

